* {{ill|Yuga Daigongen|ja|瑜伽大権現|12=draft|12=draft}} – A deity in {{ill|Shinbutsu-shūgō|ja|神仏習合|12=draft|12=draft}} (the syncretism of Shinto and Buddhism), with {{ill|Amida Nyorai|ja|阿弥陀如来|12=draft|12=draft}} (Amitābha) and {{ill|Yakushi Nyorai|ja|薬師如来|1=Bhaisajyaguru|lt=Yakushi Nyorai (Me)dicine Buddha|12=draft|12=draft}} (Bhaiṣajyaguru) as its {{ill|Honjibutsu|ja|本地仏|12=draft|12=draft}} (original Buddhist counterparts). * An alternate name for {{ill|Yuga Mountain|ja|由加山|12=draft|12=draft}} or a collective name for the two shrines below, which enshrine the above deity. ** An alternate name and enshrined deity of {{ill|Rendaiji (Kurashiki)|ja|蓮台寺 (倉敷市)|12=draft|12=draft}}. ** An alternate name and enshrined deity of {{ill|Yuga Shrine Hongū|ja|由加神社本宮|12=draft|12=draft}} and its affiliated branch shrines: *** {{ill|Yuga Daigongen (Asakuchi)|ja|由加大権現 (浅口市)|12=draft|12=draft}} – Located in {{ill|Asakuchi, Okayama|ja|浅口市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Okayama Prefecture|ja|岡山県|12=draft|12=draft}}, in {{ill|Kamogata|ja|鴨方町|12=draft|12=draft}}. *** {{ill|Yuga Daigongen (Jinseki Kōgen)|ja|由加大権現 (神石高原町)|12=draft|12=draft}} – Located in {{ill|Jinseki Kōgen, Hiroshima|ja|神石高原町|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Jinseki District|ja|神石郡|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Hiroshima Prefecture|ja|広島県|12=draft|12=draft}}. *** {{ill|Yuga Daigongen (Onomichi)|ja|由加大権現 (尾道市)|12=draft|12=draft}} – Located in {{ill|Onomichi, Hiroshima|ja|尾道市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Hiroshima Prefecture. *** {{ill|Yuga Daigongen (Mihara)|ja|由加大権現 (三原市)|12=draft|12=draft}} – Located in {{ill|Mihara, Hiroshima|ja|三原市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Hiroshima Prefecture. *** {{ill|Yuga Daigongen (Takehara)|ja|由加大権現 (竹原市)|12=draft|12=draft}} – Located in {{ill|Takehara, Hiroshima|ja|竹原市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Hiroshima Prefecture. *** {{ill|Yuga Daigongen (Tokushima)|ja|瑜伽大権現 (徳島市)|12=draft|12=draft}} – Located in {{ill|Tokushima, Tokushima|ja|徳島市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Tokushima Prefecture|ja|徳島県|12=draft|12=draft}}. *** {{ill|Yuga Daigongen (Tokushima, second shrine)|ja|瑜伽大権現 (徳島市)|12=draft|12=draft}} – A second shrine of the same name within Tokushima City. *** {{ill|Yuga Daibosatsu|ja|瑜伽大菩薩|12=draft|12=draft}} – A shrine in Tokushima City.
