cated in [[:en:Mihara, Hiroshima|Mihara, Hiroshima]], Hiroshima Prefecture. *** {{ill|Yuga Daigongen (Takehara)|ja|由加大権現 (竹原市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yuga Daigongen (Takehara)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} – Located in [[:en:Takehara, Hiroshima|Takehara, Hiroshima]], Hiroshima Prefecture. *** {{ill|Yuga Daigongen (Tokushima)|ja|瑜伽大権現 (徳島市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yuga Daigongen (Tokushima)|qq=}} – Located in [[:en:Tokushima (city)|Tokushima, Tokushima]], [[:en:Tokushima Prefecture|Tokushima Prefecture]]. *** {{ill|Yuga Daigongen (Tokushima, second shrine)|ja|瑜伽大権現 (徳島市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yuga Daigongen (Tokushima, second shrine)|qq=}} – A second shrine of the same name within Tokushima City. *** {{ill|Yuga Daibosatsu|ja|瑜伽大菩薩|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yuga Daibosatsu|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} – A shrine in Tokushima City.
